==Chinese==
===Mandarin===
[[Pinyin]]: fănbŭ

===Etymology===
originally refered to a raven ([[烏鴉]], [[乌鸦]]) that would provide food to its mother after becoming an adult

===Verb===
'''[[反]][[哺]]'''
# to take care of one's parents when they are old
#: ''[[他們]][[很]][[多]][[人]][[心底]]，[[都]][[有]]'''反哺'''[[父母]][[的]][[強烈]][[願望]]。'' ([[Traditional Chinese]])
#: ''[[他们]][[很]][[多]][[人]][[心底]]，[[都]][[有]]'''反哺'''[[父母]][[的]][[强烈]][[愿望]]。'' ([[Simplified Chinese]])
#: ''In their hearts, a lot of them have a strong desire to '''take care of their parents when they are old'''.''
# to give back to a person or institution which has contributed to one's own growth
#: ''[[從]][[農業]][[支援]][[工業]][[到]][[工業]]'''反哺'''[[農業]] ...'' ([[Traditional Chinese]])
#: ''[[从]][[农业]][[支持]][[工业]][[到]][[工业]]'''反哺'''[[农业]] ...'' ([[Simplified Chinese]])
#: ''From agriculture supporting industry to industry '''giving back''' to agriculture ...''

